Usage of ./iterate:
  -api-key string
    	API key (or set OPENCODE_API_KEY, GEMINI_API_KEY, etc.)
  -chat
    	Start interactive REPL (default when no other mode set)
  -compact
    	Compact loaded session before running
  -evolve
    	Run one evolution session (non-interactive)
  -gh-owner string
    	GitHub repo owner
  -gh-repo string
    	GitHub repo name
  -issue-limit int
    	Max community issues to include (default 5)
  -load-session string
    	Load agent messages from JSON file before run
  -model string
    	Model to use
  -phase string
    	Evolution phase: plan, implement, communicate, or "" (all)
  -provider string
    	Provider to use (anthropic, openai, groq, gemini) (default "gemini")
  -reply-issues
    	Post bot replies to addressed issues (default true)
  -repo string
    	Path to the repo iterate will evolve (default ".")
  -save-session string
    	Save agent messages to JSON file after run
  -social
    	Run social loop only (no evolution)
  -thinking string
    	Extended thinking depth: off, minimal, low, medium, high (default "off")
